						<summary>

						<p>This inscription is incomplete and damaged. It seems to register a gift for special food offerings (<hi rend="italic">peruntiruvamudhu</hi>) to Śrī Pōndaip-perumānaḍigaḷ during a particular festival day (<hi rend="italic">peruviṟṟaināḷ</hi>) by an individual called Jāthavēda-kramavittaṉ of Paṟiyalūr.</p>						

